```

Available language constants include `LANGUAGE_ENGLISH`, `LANGUAGE_CHINESE`, `LANGUAGE_FRENCH`, `LANGUAGE_GERMAN`, `LANGUAGE_JAPANESE`, `LANGUAGE_KOREAN`, `LANGUAGE_SPANISH`, `LANGUAGE_RUSSIAN`, and `LANGUAGE_PORTUGUESE`.

